00:00:01.070 --> 00:00:03.100
Let's talk about number lines.

00:00:03.100 --> 00:00:05.950
Number lines like this one
help us to visualize numbers.

00:00:05.950 --> 00:00:09.620
There are certain things that
a good number line should have.

00:00:09.620 --> 00:00:11.060
What do you think they are?

00:00:11.060 --> 00:00:15.184
Arrows on each end, zero,
marks to indicate scale,

00:00:15.184 --> 00:00:18.320
positive &amp; negative direction.

